I meant like when you are in
elementary school and

25
00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:10.760
they make you go to art class and
you’re like, primary colors.

26
00:01:11.970 --> 00:01:15.935
Primary colors are colors that cannot
be created by combining other colors.

27
00:01:15.935 --> 00:01:18.785
So in this case it's red,
yellow, and blue.

28
00:01:21.635 --> 00:01:25.475
Secondly colors are result from
mixing two different primary colors.

29
00:01:25.475 --> 00:01:27.355
So if you mix red and blue you get purple.

30
00:01:27.355 --> 00:01:29.805
If you mix green and
