43
00:02:02.842 --> 00:02:04.666
We've got monochromatic,

44
00:02:04.666 --> 00:02:09.080
they are created by establishing
variations on a shade of one color.

45
00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:12.360
These are generally very
safe color palettes.

46
00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:15.950
